<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="how-does-this-synthesis-affect-turkish-culture">How does this synthesis affect Turkish culture?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Enriches! Both traditional arts (ebru, calligraphy) and modern cinema/music develop together. This adds dynamism and diversity to Turkish culture.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you are thinking of studying in Turkey, this information will help you make informed decisions and embark on an exciting journey!</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-10-08T14:15:39Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T18:40:31Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/the-coexistence-of-traditional-and-modern-values.webp","alt":"Elderly and young Turkish people interacting in a courtyard, blending tradition and modernity","title":"the-coexistence-of-traditional-and-modern-values-__"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'traditional-and-modern-values' );
