<h3>What is artificial intelligence? Give 5 examples.</h3>
<p>ChatGPT, Google Translate, Siri, Duolingo, and the Netflix recommendation system can be given as examples of artificial intelligence.</p></p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2026-06-17T11:00:00Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-16T19:53:22Z') WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'using-ai-and-technology-to-learn-turkish' );
